{"id": 2732, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x丝芙兰】红色对于你新一年的寓意是什么？", "description": "一种气势如虹的愿景。", "record_count": 12310, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190110205941Zr26eiOzm4BwbckN.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 322304, "content": "年龄越大越喜欢张扬的颜色", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555576}, {"id": 322560, "content": "我希望中国人眼中的血液变回红色（指游戏）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343477}, {"id": 322306, "content": "嗯……怎么说，我爸秋衣的颜色", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555608}, {"id": 322307, "content": "过年，喜庆。每年过年都要穿红色的衣服或是佩戴红色的饰品。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504102}, {"id": 322308, "content": "第一眼总感觉是   阿玛尼405…", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1550419}, {"id": 322309, "content": "红色是今年元旦与ta袒露心声的那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555612}, {"id": 322822, "content": "气场全开", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1558394}, {"id": 322312, "content": "红色是一种自信，一种气质！一种热情活泼！", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551328}, {"id": 337929, "content": "心\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631103}, {"id": 322315, "content": "对一切未知怀有热情", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555668}, {"id": 322316, "content": "nothing", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 322577, "content": "明亮色的复兴冷色调的衰落", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282958}, {"id": 322323, "content": "一种新的风格 （会去跟着换种生活方式的那种）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191455}, {"id": 322324, "content": "僅僅是顏色，太多迷信和痴狂，除了cocky的nothing。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016608}, {"id": 322325, "content": "红色——耳目一新，新的一年所有全部更新！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459412}, {"id": 322326, "content": "作为一个警校生 红色意味着党吧。 希望中国越来越好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543755}, {"id": 322328, "content": "红红火火过大年 勇往直前过日子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555847}, {"id": 322329, "content": "好像也没啥，日常就比较喜欢红色", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1548442}, {"id": 322330, "content": "红色对我意味着本命年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428289}, {"id": 322331, "content": "没什么特别的意义\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463979}, {"id": 322332, "content": "就是要过年了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434017}, {"id": 322333, "content": "红色可能会让我想到热情，代表一种勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433948}, {"id": 322593, "content": "牛市", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484804}, {"id": 322338, "content": "许一个愿望 一定会实现", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434047}, {"id": 322340, "content": "有一点虚...红色就是一种颜色吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433900}, {"id": 322341, "content": "新年不能没有红色", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433805}, {"id": 322597, "content": "面对新开始的精气神", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901471}, {"id": 322342, "content": "钱钱钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433987}, {"id": 322343, "content": "前几条....大家都认真到替丝芙兰写文案了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773145}, {"id": 322344, "content": "许原帖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433999}, {"id": 322345, "content": "彩虹🌈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433883}, {"id": 322346, "content": "青春的颜色\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434002}, {"id": 322347, "content": "气场全开的颜色", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433808}, {"id": 322351, "content": "红色代表喜庆吧\n因为一直以来家里的喜事一出现就少不了红", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179301}, {"id": 322352, "content": "红色俗气，但热闹本身就是很俗气的一件事，享受俗气。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304563}, {"id": 322097, "content": "初入职场的第一双红底高跟鞋，赋予我面对困难时披荆斩棘的勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 322353, "content": "警示、热情以及努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515596}, {"id": 322098, "content": "有种恢复出厂设置的感觉，对新的一年重新获得新的勇气吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 254, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 322099, "content": "是邂逅真爱时的脸红心跳，是奋不顾身表达爱的自信", "image": null, "praise_count": 675, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 322100, "content": "抹口红的瞬间会拥有自信的力量，昂首挺胸微笑面对一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 1332, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 322363, "content": "不喜欢红色，口红例外", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556025}, {"id": 322370, "content": "让我在新的一年找到Mr.right~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556052}, {"id": 322635, "content": "可口可乐的颜色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557898}, {"id": 322382, "content": "红红火火恍恍惚惚哈哈哈哈哈哈。做什么事都能顺利。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556075}, {"id": 322383, "content": "红色意味着新春佳节，意味着团聚和家人在一起的幸福温暖！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556077}, {"id": 322384, "content": "意味着，顺利，爆发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556081}, {"id": 322385, "content": "对新一年全新开始的期盼，希望新的一年红红火火", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556079}, {"id": 322386, "content": "必须是大红包鸭🧧～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556091}, {"id": 322387, "content": "是希望 是信仰 \n是一次次失败时的累累伤痕\n是一次次失望中的微微火光\n是永不服输的倔强与勇敢\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556088}, {"id": 322391, "content": "一年都可以喜气洋洋 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556096}]}